{"tid":488281,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple繼續撚狗 - macOS 的 root 無密碼漏洞在系統更新之後又被重啟（！）","createTime":"2017-12-03T14:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T03:11:19.000Z","uid":107023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b0385b4eed7d9614509fe795ed9f74b3fb76d213","tid":488281,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"儘管蘋果已經火速地為 macOS High Sierra 的系統管理員（root）無密碼漏洞推出補丁，不過據報在「Security Update 2017-001」修正之後，若是再裝上系統更新的話，那麼這個漏洞就會再度敞開... 實話講，這樣重啟的流程應該並不算常見，因為會需要先是升級到 macOS 10.13 之後就安裝補丁，然後才升級到 macOS 10.13.1 才會讓這個問題被重新帶回來 -- 但還是有一種情況，就是原本都忘記更新系統，卻在看到有這個 Patch 後先趕快安裝，才進行系統升級的人囉。<br />\n<br />\n解決的方法？很簡單，就是再度安裝 Security Update 2017-001 補丁。但要注意一個重點，就是由於安裝之後電腦並不會提示你重開機，但要確保修正這項問題卻絕對不能忽略這個動作，所以就是記得安裝補丁然後重開機，你的 Mac 電腦應該就會暫時避開這次的 root 密碼漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n經由:&nbsp;Engadget<br />\n<br />\n來源:&nbsp;Wired<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留言<br />\n<br />\naican<br />\n<br />\n12時<br />\n<br />\n重啟就算了，但重啟後，九成的圖片都不見，變成預設圖示！<br />\n<br />\n回覆"},{"pid":"a20e0757a62a973715ba41fb7717f5cedd15a893","tid":488281,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f0692f6a71e34d6735cc5c19cd6987557fb4c2","tid":488281,"uid":37688,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"Apple野呢 就一定係整好先放出黎<br />\n今次好明顯係用家問題"},{"pid":"f94e9bc04c21c2b5da494d50d2d68e9b293840bd","tid":488281,"uid":39601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以今個星期idog好乖<br />\n無出黎吠"},{"pid":"cfcbcb76c399f2b33dfbfa6eb6bb891d69b45e8c","tid":488281,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"apple呢排做咩 個ios11 d bugs多到on9 fix極都fix唔晒 macOS就搞個咁嚴重既security flaw"},{"pid":"7c25d648c59086b76d8833e93af4a97b0078c2f3","tid":488281,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以今個星期idog好乖<br />\n無出黎吠</blockquote><br />\n比少少時間人地認清現實"},{"pid":"8d7a7e287e076ca97d52168c474e05ffe73216ac","tid":488281,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:29:50.000Z","msg":"柒夠未呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59d296136ec5b3e9b6091d8d67e484dbea4962f","tid":488281,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"同我無version control 果啲pj 差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我開始覺得如果我去apple in 一定請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4842c8c73d589016407e3a196d99870332cf39f","tid":488281,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"Windows 10用家開心使用中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}